metadata.Plot: A CIA assassin attempts to break out of the contract killing business to try to lead a normal life. But when "the system" tracks her down and frames her for the death of her husband, she embarks on a path of revenge that leads her back into the life she tried to hard to abandon.
metadata.Actors: Frida Farrell, Nick Mancuso, Rhett Giles
